## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in the field of child psychology and divorce. Additionally, the lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the currency of the information. Further research, including academic studies and expert interviews, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.